Detailed Description

cvmx_pip_hg_pri_qos

Notes: This register controls accesses to the HG_QOS_TABLE. To write an entry of the table, write PIP_HG_PRI_QOS with PRI=table address, QOS=priority level, UP_QOS=1. To read an entry of the table, write PIP_HG_PRI_QOS with PRI=table address, QOS=dont_carepriority level, UP_QOS=0 and then read PIP_HG_PRI_QOS. The table data will be in PIP_HG_PRI_QOS[QOS].
